#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.all.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.all"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:1 of
msgid "Test whether all array elements along a given axis evaluate to True."
msgstr "测试给定轴上的所有数组元素是否都为 True。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:3 of
msgid "Input tensor or object that can be converted to a tensor."
msgstr "输入张量或可转换为张量的对象。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:5 of
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which a logical AND reduction is performed. The "
"default (`axis` = `None`) is to perform a logical AND over all the "
"dimensions of the input array. `axis` may be negative, in which case it "
"counts from the last to the first axis.  If this is a tuple of ints, a "
"reduction is performed on multiple axes, instead of a single axis or all "
"the axes as before."
msgstr ""
"执行逻辑与归约操作的轴或轴的元组。默认值（`axis` = `None`）是对输入数组的"
"所有维度执行逻辑与操作。`axis` 可以为负数，在这种情况下它从最后一个轴开始"
"向前计数。如果这是一个整数元组，则在多个轴上执行归约，而不是像以前那样在"
"单个轴或所有轴上执行。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:5 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which a logical AND reduction is performed. The "
"default (`axis` = `None`) is to perform a logical AND over all the "
"dimensions of the input array. `axis` may be negative, in which case it "
"counts from the last to the first axis."
msgstr ""
"执行逻辑与归约操作的轴或轴的元组。默认值（`axis` = `None`）是对输入数组的"
"所有维度执行逻辑与操作。`axis` 可以为负数，在这种情况下它从最后一个轴开始"
"向前计数。如果这是一个整数元组，则在多个轴上执行归约，而不是像以前那样在"
"单个轴或所有轴上执行。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:10 of
msgid ""
"If this is a tuple of ints, a reduction is performed on multiple axes, "
"instead of a single axis or all the axes as before."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:13 of
msgid ""
"Alternate output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape as the expected output and its type is preserved (e.g., if "
"``dtype(out)`` is float, the result will consist of 0.0's and 1.0's).  "
"See `doc.ufuncs` (Section \"Output arguments\") for more details."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。它的形状必须与预期输出相同，并且其类型会被"
"保留（例如，如果 ``dtype(out)`` 是 float，则结果将由 0.0 和 1.0 组成）。"
"更多详情请参见 `doc.ufuncs`（“输出参数”部分）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:19 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the input tensor.  If the default value is passed, "
"then `keepdims` will not be passed through to the `all` method of sub-"
"classes of `ndarray`, however any non-default value will be.  If the sub-"
"classes `sum` method does not implement `keepdims` any exceptions will be"
" raised."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则被归约的轴将保留在结果中，其大小为 1。使用此选项时，"
"结果将能正确地与输入张量进行广播。如果传入默认值，则 `keepdims` 不会被"
"传递给 `ndarray` 子类的 `all` 方法，但任何非默认值会被传递。如果子类的 `"
"sum` 方法没有实现 `keepdims`，则会引发异常。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:19 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the input tensor."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.all.all:23 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If the default value is passed, then `keepdims` will not be passed "
"through to the `all` method of sub-classes of `ndarray`, however any non-"
"default value will be.  If the sub-classes `sum` method does not "
"implement `keepdims` any exceptions will be raised."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则被归约的轴将保留在结果中，其大小为 1。使用此选项时，"
"结果将能正确地与输入张量进行广播。如果传入默认值，则 `keepdims` 不会被"
"传递给 `ndarray` 子类的 `all` 方法，但任何非默认值会被传递。如果子类的 `"
"sum` 方法没有实现 `keepdims`，则会引发异常。"

